<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Chat Ups As A Service | Home</title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.css'>
    <link rel="shortcut.icon" href="favicon.ico"/>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

    <div class="hero-unit">
        <h1 class="text-center">So you want to chat someone up but you don't know what to say...<h1>
        <h2 style="color: red">Don't panic!</h2>
        <p> We've got it covered, choose one of our tried and tested chat up lines and hit submit to check out our ideas. If you like it you can send it to the lucky recipient from the next page.<br> <small> Please note that results are not guaranteed.</p>
    </div>


    <form method="post" action="/" class="form-horizontal">

            <div class="control-group">
                <label class="control-label" for="inputFrom">Your first name</label>
                <div class="controls">
                    <input type="text" name="from" id="inputFrom">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="control-group">
                <label class="control-label" for="inputTo">The recipient's first name</label>
                <div class="controls">
                    <input type="text" name="to" id="inputTo">
                </div>
            </div>


            <div class="control-group">
                <label>Chat up line</label>
                <div class="controls">
                    <select name="chat" id="inputChat">
                        <option>Drink?</option>
                        <option>Parking Ticket</option>
                        <option>Me Without You</option>
                        <option>Alphabet</option>
                        <option>Lost Number</option>
                        <option>Be Unique</option>
                        <option>Raisins</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="control-group">
                <label class="control-label" for="inputPhone" place-holder="only needed for Lost Number chat up">Your phone number <small>(only for Lost Number chat up)</small></label>
                <div class="controls">
                    <input type="text" name="number" id="inputPhone">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="control-group">
                <div class="controls">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success btn-large">Check it out</button>
                </div>
            </div>

    </form>


    <blockquote class="pull-right"><p>Please use this service responsibly</p></blockquote>

</div>

</body>

